      <section id="tarifs" class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Rates</h2>
        <div class="pricing-highlight">
          <p><strong>One night without breakfast for 2 people: 110&euro;</strong></p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- ========== PRACTICAL INFO ========== -->
      <section id="infos" class="section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Practical info</h2>

        <h3>Duration</h3>
        <p>Arrival between 5pm and 7pm. Departure by 10:30am the next day at the latest.</p>

        <h3>Opening</h3>
        <p>All year round.</p>

        <h3>Description</h3>
        <p>Height 5m. Access via a staircase built into a tree trunk. Private terrace approx. 4m2 facing the sea. Treehouse approx. 16m2.</p>

        <h3>Comfort</h3>
        <p>Composting toilet, electricity, cold water, kettle, heating in winter, parking 20m away.</p>

        <h3>Terrace facilities</h3>
        <p>Table, 2 chairs, lighting.</p>

        <h3>Treehouse facilities</h3>
        <p>Double bed, bedside lamps, pillows, sheets and duvet, fleece blanket, table, stools, kettle, wardrobe-bookcase, 2-seat sofa, washstand, linen provided. Children's extra mattress on request.</p>

        <h3>Getting here</h3>
        <p>On the Rennes-Brest route (RN12), between Saint-Brieuc and Lamballe, exit at Saint-Rene towards Pleneuf Val Andre. In Planguenoual, head towards the church then Chateau-Domaine du Val. Small lane on the right opposite the castle entrance.</p>
      </section>

